data.description: Wooooooow!! Check out this cozy 4Bd home, literally walking distance to the newly constructed West Jr High & Bragg Elementary! This home has a nice size living area complimented with hardwood floors that runs through out the home. This home also has tons of cabinets, closets, and storage area!! There's several things a family would love about this home! Wait until you see the large fence in back yard!!!!!
